snippet.title: Warsow 1.0 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.warsow.net/ Warsow is a completely free fast-paced first-person shooter (FPS) available for Windows, Linux and Mac OS X. Warsow is set in a futuristic cartoonish world where rocketlauncher-wielding pigs and lasergun-carrying cyberpunks roam the streets. Speed and movement is what Warsow is all about. Like a true cyberathlete you jump, dash, dodge, and walljump your way through the game. Grab power-ups before your enemy does, plant a bomb before anyone sees you, and steal the enemy's flag before they know what is going on!

Trailer by decap and KILLME courtesy of Torn Productions @ http://tornproductions.org/ and Cho-Media @ http://cho-media.org/ respectively.
Soundtrack by Ulrich Gollick @ http://soundcloud.com/voxsola
